like":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"041ef9d94b1241cee6fe6f4f3e671e89ee2765f6","tid":1869112,"uid":14449,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:30:54.000Z","msg":"全職林鄭追擊手<br />\n發覺呢排未有藍絲kol搵沈教授挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"屈婦人好似有<br />\n<br />\nBtw henry 同徐家健都有唔開名咁單單打打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"有忽然愛港的國際關係KOL一秒KO林鄭禁湖北居民入境，是扮做嘢。一時離港換跑道，一時放眼大灣區，如此唔連戲KOL何嘗不是扮KO的L。其實，香港不少所謂關鍵意見領袖，都只是大眾意見追隨者。批評別人討好北京呃飯食，難道忽然討好民粹呃like很高尚？當市場對罵林鄭罵得夠娛樂性的需求增加，罵林鄭的供應量便會上升。不要誤會，討好大眾可以是很好的娛樂，但娛樂再好，都只是大灣區同胞口中的網紅，網紅的意見毋須關鍵，尾巴主義更違反領導群眾原則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200128&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60534310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200128%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60534310&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=3829a197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200128%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60534310&h=c27b361c\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200128&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60534310</a><br />\n<br />\n成段都係批鬥，講動機<br />\n而唔係講沈生講得啱唔啱<br />\n完全冇學者風範<br />\n<br />\n徐教授近墨者黑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799b3c710416412f3a401c8e0e537cc1be38db27","tid":1869112,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"Logistics 中文係咩"},{"pid":"56e93a03d58cc846d0da058f373628157a147351","tid":18